procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFAmountWithCalculatedCurrency) var AnnualInterest : Num8 var debug : Pointer var BillLinePeriod : Num8 var InterestOnPeriod : Num8 var MonthOnPeriod : Num8 var MonthOnQuater : Num8 var MonthOnSemiAnnual : Num8 var MonthOnAnnual : Num8
MonthOnQuater = 3.0 MonthOnSemiAnnual = 6.0 MonthOnAnnual = 12.0 ; debug = Risky.OpenDebug MonthOnPeriod = self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(self.BillLine__EffectiveDate, self.BillLine__EndDate) AnnualInterest = 0.074 if MonthOnPeriod < 1 ; Monthly InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 12.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(self.BillLine__EndDate, self.CurrentDate)) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else if MonthOnPeriod < MonthOnQuater ; Quaterly InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 4.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(self.BillLine__EndDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnQuater) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else if BillLinePeriod < MonthOnSemiAnnual ; Semi-Annually InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 2.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(self.BillLine__EndDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnSemiAnnual) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else ; Annually InterestOnPeriod = AnnualInterest Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(self.BillLine__EndDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnAnnual) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount endIf endIf endIf endProc

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) if (self.Dividend__Type = cpsPayOut) or (self.Dividend__Type = cpsReduceLoanAmount) or (self.Dividend__Type = cpsPayLoanInterest) if not self.Contract__IsMEC ; the cost basis is decreased and the gain is increased Result = -self.Dividend__Amount else if self.Coverage__Gain > 0 if self.Coverage__Gain < self.Dividend__Amount ; if dividends are greater than gain, taxes are paid on gain and the gains go into the cost basis Result = -self.Dividend__Amount + self.Coverage__Gain else ; if dividends are less than gain, taxes are paid on dividends and the dividends go into the cost basis Result = -self.Dividend__Amount + self.Dividend__Amount endIf else Result = -self.Dividend__Amount endIf endIf elseif self.Dividend__Type = cpsAccumulation if not self.Contract__IsMEC Result = 0 else if self.Coverage__Gain > 0 if self.Coverage__Gain < self.Dividend__Amount Result = self.Coverage__Gain else Result = self.Dividend__Amount endIf else Result = 0 endIf endIf elseif self.Dividend__Type = cpsPaidUpAddition Result = 0 elseif self.Dividend__Type = cpsPremiumReduction Result = -self.Dividend__Amount endIf endProc

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) var NbYears : Int4 var NbDays : Num8 var policyAnniversaryDate : tWFDate var CVFactor_LastAnniversary : Num8 var CVFactor_NextAnniversary : Num8 var SurrenderMxAttainedAge : Num8 var SurrenderDxAttainedAge : Num8 var SurrenderMxAttainedAgePlus1 : Num8 var SurrenderDxAttainedAgePlus1 : Num8 var SurrenderMxFactor : Num8 var SurrenderDxFactor : Num8 var TermMxFactor : Num8 var TermMxAttainedAge : Num8 var TermMxAttainedAgePlus1 : Num8 var RPUCVFactorAttainedAge : Num8 var RPUCVFactorAttainedAgePlus1 : Num8 var unit : Num8 var PUA_FaceAmount : Num8 var NSPFactor : Num8
if self.Coverage__TerminationDate <= self.CurrentDate Result = 0 else if self.Option__CashValueStatus = cvInsidePUA ; Calculate Face amount for PUA (NToday, n Business Data) ; Dividend Paid up Additional: dividend amount / (NSP Factor / 1000) NSPFactor = self.NSP_Net_Single_Premium(self.Insured__Age__Exact, self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus) if NSPFactor <> 0 PUA_FaceAmount = self.Option__PaidUpPremiumAmount / (NSPFactor / 1000) endIf if PUA_FaceAmount <> 0 unit = PUA_FaceAmount / 1000 endIf else unit = self.Coverage__CoverageAmountAtDate(self.Option__CoverageAmountEffectiveDate) / 1000 endIf ; policyAnniversaryDate = self.Contract__ValidationDate ; number of years between the calculation date and the effective date of the policy NbYears = self.NumberOfYearsBetweenTwoDates(policyAnniversaryDate, self.CurrentDate) ; ; policy Anniversay Date self.IncYears(NbYears, policyAnniversaryDate) ; ; number of days between the policy anniverary date and the calculation date NbDays = self.CurrentDate - policyAnniversaryDate ; if self.Contract__IsReduced(self.CurrentDate) ; Surrender a RPU policy ;Mx/Dx attained age SurrenderMxAttainedAge = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears, Mx) SurrenderDxAttainedAge = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears, Dx) ;Mx/Dx attained age +1 SurrenderMxAttainedAgePlus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears + 1, Mx) SurrenderDxAttainedAgePlus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears + 1, Dx) ; ; RPU Mx Factor RPUCVFactorAttainedAge = SurrenderMxAttainedAge / SurrenderDxAttainedAge * 1000 ; ; RPU Dx Factor RPUCVFactorAttainedAgePlus1 = SurrenderMxAttainedAgePlus1 / SurrenderDxAttainedAgePlus1 * 1000 ; ; ************ ; Cash Value on an RPU policy ; ************ Result = (RPUCVFactorAttainedAge + (RPUCVFactorAttainedAgePlus1 - RPUCVFactorAttainedAge) * (NbDays / self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear)) * unit ; elseif self.Option__CashValueStatus = cvETI ; ETI ; ; ************ ; ETI Factor at Surrender Date ; ************ ;Mx/Dx attained age SurrenderMxAttainedAge = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears, Mx) SurrenderDxAttainedAge = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears, Dx) ;Mx/Dx attained age +1 SurrenderMxAttainedAgePlus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears + 1, Mx) SurrenderDxAttainedAgePlus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears + 1, Dx) ; ; ETI Mx Factor SurrenderMxFactor = SurrenderMxAttainedAge + (SurrenderMxAttainedAgePlus1 - SurrenderMxAttainedAge) * (NbDays / self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear) ; ; ETI Dx Factor SurrenderDxFactor = SurrenderDxAttainedAge + (SurrenderDxAttainedAgePlus1 - SurrenderDxAttainedAge) * (NbDays / self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear) ; ; ************ ; ETI Factor at Termination Date ; ************ ; ; number of years between the Termination date and the effective date of the policy ; !!!!!!!!!!!! Wait Planned Termination Date Data NbYears = self.NumberOfYearsBetweenTwoDates(self.Contract__ValidationDate, self.Coverage__TerminationDate) ; ; policy Anniversay Date self.IncYears(NbYears, policyAnniversaryDate) ; ; number of days between the policy anniverary date (Termination) and the calculation date NbDays = self.Coverage__TerminationDate - policyAnniversaryDate ; ;Mx/Dx attained age TermMxAttainedAge = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears, Mx) ;Mx/Dx attained age +1 TermMxAttainedAgePlus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears + 1, Mx) ; ETI Mx Factor TermMxFactor = TermMxAttainedAge + (TermMxAttainedAgePlus1 - TermMxAttainedAge) * (NbDays / self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear) ; ; ************ ; Cash Value on an ETI policy ; ************ ; Result = (SurrenderMxFactor - TermMxFactor) / SurrenderDxFactor * unit else ; Cash value Factor last anniversary CVFactor_LastAnniversary = self.CSO2001_Blended_5_(NbYears, self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription) ; Cash value Factor next anniversary CVFactor_NextAnniversary = self.CSO2001_Blended_5_(NbYears + 1, self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription) ; ; Cash Value if NbDays = 0 Result = CVFactor_LastAnniversary * unit else Result = (CVFactor_LastAnniversary + (CVFactor_NextAnniversary - CVFactor_LastAnniversary) * (NbDays / self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear)) * unit endIf Result = self.RoundToNearest(Result, 0.01) endIf endIf endProc

; RPU if self.Option__CashValueStatus = cvReduction unit = self.Coverage__CoverageAmountAtDate(self.CurrentDate) / 1000 ; policyAnniversaryDate = self.Contract__ValidationDate ; number of years between the calculation date and the effective date of the policy NbYears = self.NumberOfYearsBetweenTwoDates(policyAnniversaryDate, self.CurrentDate) ; ; policy Anniversay Date self.IncYears(NbYears, policyAnniversaryDate) ; ; number of days between the policy anniverary date and the calculation date NbDays = self.CurrentDate - policyAnniversaryDate ; CV = self.Option__TotalCashValueAndTabularAtDate(self.CurrentDate) - self.Option__TotalUnPaidLoanAmount ; ;Mx/Dx attained age MxAttainedAge = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears, Mx) DxAttainedAge = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears, Dx) ;Mx/Dx attained age +1 MxAttainedAgePlus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears + 1, Mx) DxAttainedAgePlus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription + NbYears + 1, Dx) ; RPUFactor = ((self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear - NbDays) * (MxAttainedAge / DxAttainedAge) + NbDays * (MxAttainedAgePlus1 / DxAttainedAgePlus1)) / self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear ;RPU Result = self.RoundToNearest(CV / unit / RPUFactor * unit, 1) if Result < 0 Result = 0 endIf self.AppendPossibleValue(tWFAmount(Result)) elseif self.Option__CashValueStatus = cvInsidePUA ; Dividend Paid up Additional: dividend amount / (NSP Factor / 1000) Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount + self.Option__PaidUpPremiumAmount / (self.NSP_Net_Single_Premium(self.Insured__Age__Exact, self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus) / 1000) else self.SetFreeChoice for i = 50000 to 250000 step 10000 self.AppendPossibleValue(tWFAmount(i)) endFor endIf endProc

; loop on commutation table to find the closest min ETIMx calculated age = 0 while age < 120 tmpMx = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(age, Mx) if MxETI >= tmpMx break endIf age += 1 endWhile ; if age = 120 Result = self.CurrentDate exit endIf ; ; calculate the policy duration associated at the ETIMx duration = age - self.Insured__Age__Nearest_At_Subscription ; ; Number of year from the ETI Date ETIYear = duration - 1 - NbYears ; MxETIMinus1 = self.CommutationTables_2001_Blended_5_(age - 1, Mx) ; ; ********************************************************************* ; Death benefit outside the exclusion period ; ********************************************************************* ; Face amount on the Base (include Paid up addition) Death_Benefit = self.Coverage__CoverageAmountAtDate(self.Death__DeathDate) ; ; + Post Mortem Interest Number_of_Days = self.CurrentDate - self.Death__DeathDate Post_Mortem_Interest = Death_Benefit * self.Post_Mortem_Interest_Rate_Per_State(self.Subscriber__PersonResidenceState) * (Number_of_Days / self.NumberOfDaysInCurrentYear) ; self.AppendComment(Concat('Post Mortem Interest: ', Post_Mortem_Interest)) Death_Benefit += Post_Mortem_Interest ; ; + Dividend accumulation Death_Benefit += self.Option__CashValueAtDate(self.CurrentDate) ; ; ********************************************************************* ; Event= suicide and inside the suicide exclusion period => return the premium already paid ; ********************************************************************* PolicyAnniversaryDate = self.Contract__ValidationDate PaidPremiumToday = self.Contract__PaidPremiumToDay TotalUnPaidLoanAmount = self.Option__TotalUnPaidLoanAmount ExclPer = self.Suicide_Exclusion_Period(self.Subscriber__PersonResidenceState) self.IncYears(Int4(ExclPer), PolicyAnniversaryDate) ; if (self.Loss__Event = 'SUIC') and (self.Death__DeathDate < PolicyAnniversaryDate) self.AppendComment(Concat('Suicide - Return of premium ', PaidPremiumToday.type.AsCString(@PaidPremiumToday))) Death_Benefit = self.Contract__PaidPremiumToDay endIf ; ; - unpaid loan self.AppendComment(Concat('Unpaid Loan ', TotalUnPaidLoanAmount.type.AsCString(@TotalUnPaidLoanAmount))) Result = Death_Benefit - self.Option__TotalUnPaidLoanAmount endProc

Event of Death is a Suicide during the suicide exclusion period: Death benefit=return of the premium already paid on the policy/Number of Insured Else Death benefit=Base face amount
Suicide exlusion period: This Rider does not cover suicide by an Insured Child for two years (in CO, and ND, within one year) after the Rider Date. In the event of suicide by the Insured Child during that period, Our payment will be limited to a refund of all premiums paid for this Rider proportionally for that Insured Child.
aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLI_LifeDisabilityRuleEngine) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFCountryTypes, WFTypes, aWFRuleDesc
function Suicide_Exclusion_Period(ApplicationSignedStates : tWFUSState) return tWFNum8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(ApplicationSignedStates, 0, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) var Death_Benefit : Num8 var PolicyAnniversaryDate : tWFDate var ExclPer : Num8
; Death benefit outside the exclusion period => Face amount on the Base Death_Benefit = self.Coverage__CoverageAmountAtDate(self.Death__DeathDate) ; ; Event= suicide and inside the suicide exclusion period => return the premium already paid / Number of Insured on the option PolicyAnniversaryDate = self.Contract__ValidationDate ExclPer = self.Suicide_Exclusion_Period(self.Subscriber__PersonResidenceState) self.IncYears(Int4(ExclPer), PolicyAnniversaryDate) ; if (self.Loss__Event = 'SUIC') and (self.Death__DeathDate < PolicyAnniversaryDate) Death_Benefit = self.Contract__PaidPremiumToDay / self.Coverage__CoveredNumber endIf ; Result = Death_Benefit endProc
